Senate Resolution 162
By: Senator Kennedy of the 18th
A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Shermet Sims, recipient of the LPN of the Year award; and
2 for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, the Georgia health care association Stars in Long Term Care honors outstanding
4 long-term and post-acute care professionals for their exemplary contributions to the
5 profession and commitment to enhancing the lives of vulnerable Georgians; and
6 WHEREAS, the hardworking individuals being recognized are involved in all different areas
7 of long-term and post-acute care with one commonality: their commitment to serving elderly
8 and disabled Georgians; and
9 WHEREAS, these individuals make a difference in the lives of long-term care residents and
10 patients every single day; and
11 WHEREAS, through their care, compassion, and willingness to go above and beyond the call
12 of duty, they help make Georgia a better place for seniors; and
