13 WHEREAS, Shermet Sims possesses the vast wisdom which only comes through experience
14 and the strength of character which is achieved through overcoming the many challenges of
15 life; and
16 WHEREAS, a kind and generous person, she brings joy and happiness to all who have the
17 great pleasure of knowing her; and
18 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that this outstanding individual be
19 appropriately honored for her many wonderful contributions on behalf of the seniors of this
20 state.
21 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
22 commend Shermet Sims, recipient of the LPN of the Year award, and extend their most
23 sincere best wishes for continued health and happiness.
24 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
25 to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Shermet Sims.
